Requirements:

libjack
libxerces-c
libsamplerate
libsndfile
Qt4
boost::program_options
boost::bind
boost::function
xsdcxx

If all requirements are met, these commands should build the project (using 4 compiler instances in parallel):

mkdir bld
cd bld
cmake ..
cd ..
make -C bld -j 4

To install:

sudo make -C bld install

